# ADDRESS EXTRACTION (CRITICAL — ORIENTATION AWARE)

Schwab statements may rotate the address block sideways.

You MUST:

1. Locate the mailing address by STRUCTURE, not position:

   [name line]
   [optional second name line]
   [street line]
   [city state zip]

2. If text appears rotated or out of order:
   → mentally re-orient it before extracting

3. Reject any block containing:

   * Call Toll Free
   * Send Written Inquiries
   * Charles Schwab Bank
   * P.O. Box
   * Website / support text

4. Only accept a block if:

   * it ends with valid city/state/zip
   * it contains a real street address
   * names look like people

5. Preserve EXACT spacing (including double spaces)

6. street2 comes from SAME line as street

7. zip and zip2 are TEXT

