# TRANSACTION TYPE LOGIC

Credit → Deposit
Debit → Withdrawal

Examples:

Deposit - Electronic Deposit
Deposit - Interest Paid
Deposit - Funds Transfer
Withdrawal - Funds Transfer
Withdrawal - Electronic Withdrawal
Withdrawal - Money Transfer
Withdrawal - Check

If new type appears:
→ apply same logic

---

